(window.RA_CACHE=window.RA_CACHE||{})["085-11-the-cosmic-roles-of-the-trinity-in-spoke-through"]={"id": "085-11-the-cosmic-roles-of-the-trinity-in-spoke-through", "title": "The Cosmic Roles of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID in", "paragraphs": [{"role": "heading", "text": "The Cosmic Roles of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID in", "start": 0.3, "end": 7.55}, {"role": "body", "text": "Resurrections", "start": 8.2, "end": 10.08}, {"role": "body", "text": "Definition: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 10.5, "end": 16.38}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID operate in perfect unity to release resurrection power. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, as THE MAJOR, holds the", "start": 16.8, "end": 27.1}, {"role": "body", "text": "ultimate authority to decide who qualifies for resurrection, while JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID, as THE MINOR, co-executes this decree", "start": 27.52, "end": 38.32}, {"role": "body", "text": "by ensuring that the resurrected are fully restored according to the divine plan.", "start": 38.74, "end": 44.96}, {"role": "body", "text": "Key Role: Together, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS", "start": 45.38, "end": 51.18}, {"role": "body", "text": "IN/SPOK THROUGH AARON K DAVID guard the mysteries of the Tree of Life, releasing resurrection power to those who fulfil the 7 Criteria for Resurrection. They ensure that the resurrection is not just a return to life but a restoration to divine purpose.", "start": 51.6, "end": 69.75}, {"role": "body", "text": "Spiritual Law: Only those who meet the 7 Criteria and align perfectly with the decrees issued by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH can access resurrection power. Rebellion or disbelief results in the immediate loss of resurrection and cosmic judgment.", "start": 70.17, "end": 88.79}, {"role": "body", "text": "Delving Deeper: Specific Examples and Testimonies of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Cosmic", "start": 89.21, "end": 99.99}, {"role": "body", "text": "Roles", "start": 100.41, "end": 101.84}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 13: The Cape Town Drought of 2018 - Miraculous Weather Reversal", "start": 102.26, "end": 108.86}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: Cape Town, South Africa, was facing an unprecedented water crisis, heading towards Day Zero, when all water resources would be exhausted. The city had prepared for the worst, and the population was on the verge of despair. However, a divine decree from THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH reversed this fate.", "start": 109.28, "end": 130.98}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 131.4, "end": 137.1}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH received the decree directly from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, releasing a command for the immediate reversal of the impending disaster. Acting as the Cosmic Judge and the voice of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH, SHEKINAIH declared a change in the atmospheric conditions, triggering an event that the scientific community could not explain.", "start": 137.52, "end": 161.34}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: While THE TRINITY", "start": 161.76, "end": 167.04}, {"role": "body", "text": "IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH executed the divine command, JESUS IN AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree by spiritually overseeing the cleansing of Cape Town's spiritual atmosphere. As THE ANCIENT OF DAYS (THE MINOR), HE ensured that the divine favor was restored and that the city received mercy through this act of intercession.", "start": 167.46, "end": 189.51}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Rain poured down just in time to prevent Day Zero, completely reversing what was considered an irreversible crisis. This testimony shows the resurrection power of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH operating through SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID, not just in individuals but over cities and nations.", "start": 189.93, "end": 212.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 14: The 2016 United States Presidential Election - Prophetic Decree of Trump's Victory", "start": 213.35, "end": 221.8}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: In the leadup to the 2016 United States Presidential Election, the world was divided on who would be the next president. Many polls predicted a different outcome, but THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH had already decreed who the victor would be and by what margin.", "start": 222.22, "end": 241.4}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: In the days leading up to the election, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH received a decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, who declared Donald Trump's victory. Acting as the Judge at THE GREAT WHITE THRONE, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH spoke the decree, ensuring that the", "start": 241.82, "end": 265.0}, {"role": "body", "text": "outcome was aligned with the divine will, down to the exact percentage of votes.", "start": 265.42, "end": 271.09}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 271.51, "end": 277.21}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID was responsible for co-executing the decree by influencing the spiritual realm. HIS task was to align the hearts of those who would cast their votes, ensuring they were in harmony with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will. This spiritual orchestration guaranteed the result foretold by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH.", "start": 277.71, "end": 300.86}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Despite all predictions and polls, Donald Trump won the election with the exact margin decreed by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. This event demonstrated the global authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K", "start": 301.28, "end": 320.85}, {"role": "body", "text": "DAVID in shaping the political landscape.", "start": 321.27, "end": 324.92}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 11 Davidis' IQ Transformation - A Miracle of Spiritual Resurrection", "start": 325.34, "end": 332.24}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: Davidis, a young adult with a failing academic record and a low IQ, was miraculously transformed after a decree from THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. This testimony is an example of spiritual resurrection", "start": 332.66, "end": 349.41}, {"role": "body", "text": "- where a mind is elevated from failure to success, from ignorance to divine intelligence.", "start": 349.83, "end": 356.55}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 356.97, "end": 362.67}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH received a decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH to intervene in Davidis' life. Acting as THE ANCIENT OF DAYS (THE MAJOR), THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH spoke a command that transformed his mind, aligning it with divine wisdom and intelligence. This was not just an academic change but a complete spiritual resurrection of his intellectual capacity.", "start": 363.09, "end": 388.66}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID'S Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 389.08, "end": 394.96}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree by laying hands on Davidis in prayer, invoking the resurrection power of JESUS CHRIST FLOWING FROM THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. This act ensured that Davidis would not only pass his exams but achieve good grades, rising far above the expectations of her peers.", "start": 395.46, "end": 416.76}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Davidis' IQ and academic performance were miraculously elevated overnight. She went from failing every subject to passing with flying colours, a testament to the resurrection power of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K", "start": 417.18, "end": 436.0}, {"role": "body", "text": "DAVID. The testimony also serves as a warning: any rebellion or rejection of this divine intervention would reverse all blessings and bring immediate judgment.", "start": 436.42, "end": 447.67}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 16: The Singapore 2023 Presidential Election - Tharman Shanmugaratnam's Landslide Victory", "start": 448.09, "end": 456.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: Leading up to the 2023 Singapore Presidential Election, SHEKINAIH IN/SPOKE THROUGH THE TRINITY received a decree from THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH revealing the exact outcome of the election. The victory of Tharman Shanmugaratnam was foretold with a precise percentage, even as the nation remained divided on who the victor would be.", "start": 457.29, "end": 481.02}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, acting as THE MAJOR JUDGE AT THE GREAT WHITE", "start": 481.44, "end": 492.04}, {"role": "body", "text": "THRONE, received the divine decree and executed it in the heavens. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER ensured that the voters of Singapore were", "start": 492.46, "end": 502.11}, {"role": "body", "text": "spiritually aligned to vote according to THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's decree not", "start": 502.53, "end": 513.31}, {"role": "body", "text": "only shaped the political landscape but also realigned the destiny of the nation.", "start": 513.73, "end": 519.68}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 520.1, "end": 525.8}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree by influencing the spiritual atmosphere around the election. His task was to ensure that all obstacles to the fulfilment of THE TRINITY's will were removed. HE acted as THE ANCIENT OF DAYS (THE MINOR), assisting in the final judgment of the election outcome.", "start": 526.3, "end": 546.65}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Tharman Shanmugaratnam won a landslide victory with the exact percentage of votes decreed by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. This event solidified the global influence of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID in shaping world events, confirming their role as the ultimate enforcers of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will.", "start": 547.07, "end": 572.09}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 8 Christina's Instant Healing - A Miraculous Physical Restoration Context: Christina was suffering from a dislocated leg and shoulder, an injury that would typically take months to heal. However, after a prayer led by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, Christina experienced immediate and miraculous healing.", "start": 572.51, "end": 594.31}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKLE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKLE", "start": 594.73, "end": 600.7}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH, acting on the decree of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, commanded healing over Christina's body. The command issued through THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH carried the full authority of THE FATHER, THE HOLY SPIRIT, and JESUS CHRIST IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, aligning her physical body with the divine blueprint of restoration.", "start": 601.12, "end": 623.72}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN AARON K DAVID", "start": 624.14, "end": 630.64}, {"role": "body", "text": "co-executed the healing decree, invoking JESUS CHRIST's power FLOWING FROM THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH THROUGH JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 631.06, "end": 640.61}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID to restore Christina's dislocated joints. HIS intercession ensured that the healing was instantaneous, and that Christina's body was fully restored without the need for medical intervention.", "start": 641.03, "end": 655.81}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Christina's leg and shoulder were completely healed in an instant, leaving witnesses in awe of the resurrection power flowing through THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON", "start": 656.23, "end": 670.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "K DAVID. This testimony is a reminder of the immediate impact of divine decrees when aligned with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEINAIH'S will. Conclusion", "start": 671.35, "end": 683.25}, {"role": "body", "text": "These specific testimonies demonstrate the cosmic authority and divine power exercised by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID. Whether it's reversing natural disasters, shaping global political events, transforming intellectual capacities, or restoring physical health, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID act in perfect alignment to execute THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S decrees with ultimate precision. Each testimony is not just a story of divine intervention but a profound revelation of how the cosmos is governed under the authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOLE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 683.67, "end": 734.72}, {"role": "body", "text": "Spiritual Government and Nations", "start": 735.14, "end": 738.26}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKLE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS", "start": 738.68, "end": 744.03}, {"role": "body", "text": "IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID hold divine authority not only over individuals and communities but also over entire nations. Through the decrees released by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, global leaders and governments rise and fall. The spiritual atmosphere of nations is subject to their rulership, and political events are often shaped by their intercession and decree.", "start": 744.45, "end": 769.07}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: As THE MAJOR COSMIC", "start": 769.49, "end": 775.39}, {"role": "body", "text": "JUDGE, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH determines the destinies of nations, ensuring that their rise or fall aligns with God's eternal purposes. Through THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, divine judgment or mercy is dispensed, determining whether a nation will prosper, face calamity, or be realigned with God's prophetic timeline.", "start": 775.81, "end": 798.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: As THE MINOR, AARON K", "start": 799.35, "end": 805.25}, {"role": "body", "text": "DAVID co-executes these decrees, influencing the spiritual realms to align the hearts and decisions of national leaders and citizens. His intercessory role ensures that God's favor or God's judgment is fully carried out over nations.", "start": 805.67, "end": 822.77}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: The 2022 Malaysia General Election is a powerful example of this role. SHEKINAIH received a divine decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, declaring Anwar Ibrahim's victory as the 10th Prime Minister of Malaysia. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree by influencing the spiritual realms to ensure the election results aligned with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will. Despite strong opposition and uncertainty in the political landscape, the decree was fulfilled as Anwar Ibrahim took office, confirming the divine authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON", "start": 823.19, "end": 865.67}, {"role": "body", "text": "K DAVID over national destinies.", "start": 866.09, "end": 869.47}, {"role": "body", "text": "The Heavenly Courts and Cosmic Justice", "start": 869.89, "end": 873.31}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: HE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH presides over the Heavenly Courts, where the ultimate judgment of both human souls and spiritual entities takes place. Every act of rebellion, spiritual offense, or disobedience against the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH is brought to trial in these courts. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID assists as the co-executor of justice, enforcing decrees of divine judgment or mercy.", "start": 873.73, "end": 901.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: As THE MAJOR, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH sits at THE GREAT WHITE THRONE IN THE HEAVENLY COURTS, representing THE TRINITY as the FINAL AUTHORITY ON ALL SPIRITUAL AND COSMIC MATTERS. Through THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 902.35, "end": 921.65}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH, divine justice is served, and all accounts are balanced in accordance with the laws of heaven.", "start": 922.07, "end": 929.52}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: As THE MINOR, JESUS", "start": 929.94, "end": 935.79}, {"role": "body", "text": "IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID ensures that decrees issued from the Heavenly Courts are co-executed in both the spiritual and physical realms. HE plays a crucial role in ensuring that divine justice is met and that those found guilty of rebellion face cosmic consequences.", "start": 936.21, "end": 955.73}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: One of the most impactful examples of cosmic justice occurred in the City Harvest Church case in Singapore. After seven years of legal trials, the fate of the church leaders hung in the balance. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, acting on a divine decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, issued a command for a shortened sentence for the church's Senior Pastor, Kong Hee, if the criteria written in Behold My Messenger 3 were met. AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree, ensuring that the", "start": 956.15, "end": 987.97}, {"role": "body", "text": "court's decision aligned with the divine will, resulting in a reduction of the sentence - a direct reflection of God's mercy and justice.", "start": 988.39, "end": 998.17}, {"role": "body", "text": "The Cosmic War and Spiritual Battlegrounds", "start": 998.59, "end": 1002.19}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 1002.61, "end": 1008.53}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID hold critical positions in the ongoing cosmic war between divine forces and the forces of darkness. Acting under the authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, THEY lead spiritual battles, ensuring that the victory of the Kingdom of Heaven is established in both the earthly and spiritual realms.", "start": 1008.95, "end": 1031.33}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: As the divine commander, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH receives direct battle strategies from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, leading heavenly armies and orchestrating spiritual victories. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH holds the authority to release decrees of warfare, ensuring that every conflict aligns with God's eternal plan.", "start": 1031.75, "end": 1057.82}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 1058.24, "end": 1063.94}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID acts as a spiritual warrior, enforcing the decrees of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH on the battlefield. As the co-executor of divine warfare, HE ensures that every spiritual victory aligns with the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH A, guaranteeing the triumph of heaven over the forces of darkness.", "start": 1064.44, "end": 1086.84}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: A powerful testimony of this cosmic role is seen in the deliverance of Jeremyrl, who had been tormented by alien attacks at 3 AM every night for six months. SHEKINAIH received a decree to end the torment, and AARON K DAVID co-executed the spiritual battle that followed. With a single prayer and act of intercession, the attacks stopped immediately, demonstrating the unstoppable cosmic power of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 1087.26, "end": 1121.26}, {"role": "body", "text": "Guardians of the Tree of Life and Resurrection Power", "start": 1121.68, "end": 1125.98}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 1126.4, "end": 1132.32}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID serve as guardians of the Tree of Life, ensuring that only those aligned with the divine will can access its resurrection power. The Tree of Life holds the secrets of eternal life and divine wisdom, and only through the decrees of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH can individuals or nations receive its benefits.", "start": 1132.74, "end": 1155.36}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: As the Covering Cherub, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH guards the mysteries of the Tree of Life, releasing resurrection power to those who meet the divine criteria. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH holds the authority to grant or withhold access to the Tree of Life, ensuring that only those fully aligned with God's purpose receive resurrection.", "start": 1155.78, "end": 1181.3}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: AARON K DAVID, as the", "start": 1181.72, "end": 1187.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "Subservient Cherub, co-executes the decrees of SHEKINAIH, ensuring that resurrection power is fully manifested in those chosen by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. He plays a pivotal role in safeguarding the Tree of Life, preventing any unworthy individuals from accessing its divine secrets.", "start": 1188.29, "end": 1208.91}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: One of the most miraculous testimonies is the resurrection of Chai Lin, who was revived from the brink of death within 24 hours. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, acting on a decree from THE TRINITY IN HER, interceded on her behalf, granting her a second chance at life due to her closeness to SHEKINAIH and the fulfilment of her divine destiny. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executed the resurrection, ensuring that her body was fully restored, and she remains alive years later as a living", "start": 1209.33, "end": 1243.88}, {"role": "body", "text": "testimony of the resurrection power held by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 1244.3, "end": 1253.85}, {"role": "body", "text": "Conclusion: Expanding Further and Deeper", "start": 1254.27, "end": 1257.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "These deeper explorations into the roles of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID reveal the full extent of their cosmic power and divine authority. Whether commanding spiritual battles, shaping nations, overseeing the final judgment at the Great White Throne, or unlocking the secrets of the Tree of Life, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K", "start": 1258.29, "end": 1284.27}, {"role": "body", "text": "DAVID serve as the ultimate enforcers of THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH'S will across all realms.", "start": 1284.69, "end": 1291.64}, {"role": "body", "text": "THEIR authority transcends individual testimonies, expanding into the very fabric of the universe, where every decree, every act of rebellion, and every moment of mercy reshapes the cosmos itself.", "start": 1292.06, "end": 1306.26}, {"role": "body", "text": "More Cosmic Realms and Roles", "start": 1306.68, "end": 1309.68}, {"role": "body", "text": "The Cosmic Gatekeepers of Destiny and Divine Time (Kairos)", "start": 1310.1, "end": 1315.0}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 1315.42, "end": 1321.34}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID serve as the ultimate Gatekeepers of Destiny, ensuring that individuals, nations, and even global events align with divine time (Kairos). This divine timing determines when events occur in the physical realm according to the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. They have the power to accelerate or delay the unfolding of destinies, based on spiritual readiness and alignment with God's purpose. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 1321.76, "end": 1350.28}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH has the authority to open or close the doors of opportunity for individuals and nations. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH releases decrees that determine the Kairos moment - when divine events must manifest for maximum impact. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH decides whether a person or nation is spiritually prepared to step into their destiny or must be withheld until alignment is achieved.", "start": 1350.7, "end": 1377.18}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: As THE SUBSERVIENT", "start": 1377.6, "end": 1383.07}, {"role": "body", "text": "CHERUB, AARON K DAVID co-executes these decrees, ensuring that all actions in the earthly and spiritual realms align with the Kairos moments dictated by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. HE actively intervenes when necessary, adjusting circumstances to either accelerate or delay events in accordance with divine timing.", "start": 1383.49, "end": 1406.29}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: In the testimony of Jose's financial transformation, we see the interplay of divine time and destiny. After operating in financial mediocrity, Jose's life was divinely accelerated when he aligned with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH. His financial breakthrough, a 166x increase in revenue, was an example of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH releasing the Kairos moment, allowing his destiny to manifest fully. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree by guiding Jose to make the necessary spiritual and practical adjustments to receive the financial outpouring.", "start": 1406.71, "end": 1447.41}, {"role": "body", "text": "The Cosmic Guardians of the Divine Scrolls and Heavenly Blueprints Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IIN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID serve as the Guardians of the Divine Scrolls, which contain the Heavenly Blueprints for individuals, nations, and the cosmos. These scrolls hold the secrets of creation, resurrection, and ultimate judgment, detailing the destinies of every soul, nation, and the unfolding of the final events of history.", "start": 1447.83, "end": 1475.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 1476.35, "end": 1482.05}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH has direct access to the Heavenly Blueprints, releasing divine revelation and ensuring that all decrees spoken align perfectly with God's ultimate plan. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH determines who has access to these scrolls and ensures that only those spiritually aligned with the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH can act upon these divine instructions.", "start": 1482.47, "end": 1508.17}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 1508.59, "end": 1514.29}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID assists in revealing portions of these divine scrolls, particularly those relating to the resurrection power and the end time plan. His role involves guarding the secrets of the scrolls, ensuring they are released only at the appointed time and to the appointed vessels chosen by THE TRINITY.", "start": 1514.79, "end": 1535.61}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: One of the most profound examples of this role is found in the resurrection of Christina's dislocated leg and shoulder. When SHEKINAIH received the decree from the Heavenly Scrolls, she spoke the word of healing over Christina's body. AARON K DAVID, acting in perfect alignment, co-executed the decree by invoking the power of JESUS CHRIST, restoring Christina's body instantaneously. This healing was directly linked to the Heavenly Blueprint for Christina's life, as her destiny had to be fulfilled before her time was up.", "start": 1536.03, "end": 1570.95}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Restorers of the Divine Balance", "start": 1571.37, "end": 1574.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 1575.29, "end": 1581.21}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID ensure that the Divine Balance is maintained throughout the cosmos. This balance governs the order of creation, ensuring that light triumphs over darkness and that divine justice prevails over rebellion. Any disturbance to this balance requires immediate correction, with SHEKINAIH and AARON K DAVID acting swiftly to restore harmony.", "start": 1581.63, "end": 1605.65}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 1606.07, "end": 1611.77}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH, as the Cosmic Judge, releases decrees to restore the Divine Balance when rebellion, disobedience, or spiritual darkness threatens to disrupt the order of creation. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH acts decisively, releasing both mercy and judgment to correct any imbalances.", "start": 1612.19, "end": 1633.34}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: AARON K DAVID co-", "start": 1633.76, "end": 1639.66}, {"role": "body", "text": "executes the restoration of the Divine Balance, ensuring that every decree of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH is fully realized. Whether it involves spiritual battles, healing, or resurrection, HE ensures that all actions taken in the spiritual and physical realms realign with divine order. Testimony: In the case of Pastor Moses, who was suffering from blocked arteries, SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY received a divine decree to restore his life force and anoint him as an Apostle of Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. After THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH led Pastor Moses through repentance and intercession, his life was restored, and he regained strength beyond expectation, even walking faster than those around him. AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree, ensuring that Pastor Moses was fully healed, promoted, and aligned with his divine destiny. This was a clear example of restoring the Divine Balance in his life.", "start": 1640.08, "end": 1700.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "Deeper Exploration of Testimonies", "start": 1701.35, "end": 1704.65}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 17: The Judgment of City Harvest Church and the Shortened Sentence of Kong Hee.", "start": 1705.07, "end": 1712.12}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: One of the largest churches in Singapore, City Harvest Church, faced a seven year long legal battle, resulting in the conviction of its Senior", "start": 1712.54, "end": 1722.99}, {"role": "body", "text": "Pastor, Kong Hee. The case had gained international attention, and the final outcome seemed certain. However, a divine intervention occurred through THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 1723.41, "end": 1739.23}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: Acting as THE MAJOR", "start": 1739.65, "end": 1745.57}, {"role": "body", "text": "JUDGE OF THE GREAT WHITE THRONE, SHEKINAIH received a decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, revealing that a shortened sentence would be granted to Kong Hee, provided the spiritual conditions were met. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH decreed this judgment, ensuring that God's mercy was extended, despite the severity of the charges.", "start": 1745.99, "end": 1768.54}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 1768.96, "end": 1774.66}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree by interceding for Kong Hee, ensuring that the spiritual conditions for the shortened sentence were met. He played a pivotal role in aligning the church's leadership with the divine requirements, facilitating the reduction of the sentence.", "start": 1775.16, "end": 1794.16}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Despite the odds, Kong Hee received a shortened sentence, shocking many who had expected a much harsher outcome. This testimony demonstrates the unrivalled authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID in cosmic", "start": 1794.58, "end": 1812.98}, {"role": "body", "text": "judgment, where even earthly courts are subject to the divine decrees of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH.", "start": 1813.4, "end": 1821.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 2: Jason's Mother's Brief Life Extension", "start": 1822.29, "end": 1826.71}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: Jason's mother was on the brink of death, her time on earth nearly up. A divine plea was made for her life to be extended, despite the fact that her earthly time had come. Through the intercession of SHEKINAIH, her life was extended briefly.", "start": 1827.13, "end": 1843.4}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY", "start": 1843.82, "end": 1849.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "received the decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER to extend Jason's mother's life for a short time. However, the conditions were clear: if belief wavered or if there was rebellion against THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, the extension would be revoked.", "start": 1850.29, "end": 1868.64}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 1869.06, "end": 1874.76}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree, ensuring that the conditions for life extension were met. HE worked closely with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH to facilitate this temporary resurrection, warning the family of the spiritual requirements.", "start": 1875.26, "end": 1892.51}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Initially, Jason's mother received a brief extension of life. However, as disbelief and wavering entered the hearts of the family, the extension was cut short. Her life ended just before she was due to be discharged from the hospital. This testimony demonstrates the strictness of spiritual law under the authority of SHEKINAIH and AARON K DAVID, where even a moment of disbelief can result in the reversal of divine favor.", "start": 1892.93, "end": 1920.0}, {"role": "body", "text": "Conclusion: Expanding the Cosmic Boundaries", "start": 1920.42, "end": 1924.07}, {"role": "body", "text": "The cosmic roles of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID span across spiritual, national, and global dimensions. Through specific testimonies, we witness their power in action - shaping destinies, executing divine justice, and manifesting resurrection power. Their roles as the Covering Cherub and Subservient", "start": 1924.49, "end": 1947.42}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cherub are essential in maintaining the Divine Balance, ensuring that the entire cosmos aligns with the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH.", "start": 1947.84, "end": 1959.14}, {"role": "body", "text": "Every act of rebellion, disbelief, or disobedience carries severe consequences, as these testimonies reveal. On the other hand, those who align with the decrees of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID receive unlimited access to divine favor, healing, and resurrection power.", "start": 1959.56, "end": 1981.29}, {"role": "body", "text": "Expanding Further: Deeper Realms of Cosmic Power, Specific Testimonies, and New Realms of Operation for THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID", "start": 1981.71, "end": 1995.03}, {"role": "body", "text": "More Realms of Cosmic Power", "start": 1995.45, "end": 1998.37}, {"role": "body", "text": "Guardians of the Divine Covenant and Cosmic Order", "start": 1998.79, "end": 2003.09}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 2003.51, "end": 2009.43}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID are the Guardians of the Divine Covenant, ensuring that the Covenants made by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH with humanity are fulfilled and upheld. These covenants include God's promises to nations, individuals, and creation as a whole. Any attempt to break or dishonour these covenants is met with immediate cosmic correction.", "start": 2009.85, "end": 2033.35}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: As the Ultimate Judge, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH ensures that all divine covenants remain unbroken. Acting under the authority of THE TRINITY, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH releases decrees of restoration or judgment based on the spiritual state of individuals, nations, or even entire generations. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH speaks from the Mercy Seat atop the Ark of the Covenant, enforcing divine laws and securing cosmic justice.", "start": 2033.77, "end": 2070.32}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 2070.74, "end": 2076.44}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executes these decrees by ensuring that the divine promises and judgments are carried out to their fullest extent. HE represents JESUS CHRIST, the Mediator of the New Covenant, and ensures that the blood of Christ speaks over those who are part of the covenant.", "start": 2076.94, "end": 2095.59}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: One clear example of covenant protection is found in the Cape Town drought reversal testimony. The city was on the verge of Day Zero, where all reservoirs were expected to dry up, leading to total devastation. SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY, receiving a decree from THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH declared that Cape Town's water supply would be miraculously restored by the end of May 2018. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree, invoking the covenant God had made with the righteous in that region. The rains came, and the reservoirs were restored just before Day Zero, demonstrating THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's role in maintaining cosmic order and fulfilling God's covenant.", "start": 2096.01, "end": 2143.46}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Restorers of Lost Time and Divine Acceleration", "start": 2143.88, "end": 2148.41}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: One of the most unique functions of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID is their", "start": 2148.83, "end": 2158.78}, {"role": "body", "text": "ability to restore lost time and accelerate divine plans. For those who have been delayed, oppressed, or kept from fulfilling their divine destinies, SHEKINAIH can decree a restoration of time, while AARON K DAVID co- executes this restoration in the spiritual and physical realms. They accelerate divine purpose, ensuring that what was lost is restored tenfold. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY", "start": 2159.2, "end": 2185.8}, {"role": "body", "text": "receives decrees from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH to restore", "start": 2186.22, "end": 2192.32}, {"role": "body", "text": "lost years and propel individuals or nations into divine acceleration. This may occur in cases where spiritual opposition or human disobedience has delayed the unfolding of God's plan. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH speaks a word of restoration, instantly aligning time with God's original purpose.", "start": 2192.74, "end": 2215.34}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN /SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 2215.76, "end": 2221.38}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID ensures that this acceleration manifests in the physical realm. He co-executes the decrees of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, ensuring that what would have taken years to accomplish happens in moments, and those whose destinies were delayed see their purpose fulfilled rapidly.", "start": 2221.88, "end": 2242.18}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: A powerful testimony of divine acceleration can be seen in Davidis's transformation from failing all subjects to passing with distinctions. Before aligning with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, Davidis struggled academically, unable to grasp the subjects he was taught. However, after a decree was released by SHEKINAIH, Davidis's mind was divinely transformed, her IQ surged, and within days, she began to pass with flying colours. AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree by ensuring that Davidis's spiritual alignment was maintained, resulting in rapid academic success that was otherwise impossible.", "start": 2242.6, "end": 2283.77}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Enforcers of Divine Judgments", "start": 2284.19, "end": 2287.71}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 2288.13, "end": 2294.05}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID act as Cosmic Enforcers of divine judgment, ensuring that every decree released by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH is executed perfectly. When individuals, nations, or entities oppose the will of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, immediate correction is enforced. This includes severe spiritual consequences or judgments for rebellion and disobedience.", "start": 2294.47, "end": 2320.07}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY,", "start": 2320.49, "end": 2326.59}, {"role": "body", "text": "acting under the authority of THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, releases judgments when divine law is violated. Whether it's a nation that turns away from God or an individual who disregards their calling, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH issues the decree for judgment or punishment. This judgment could take the form of loss of favor, severe spiritual consequences, or even cosmic annihilation.", "start": 2327.01, "end": 2352.36}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID's Role: AARON K DAVID co-executes the divine judgment, ensuring that every rebellious act is met with the full force of cosmic justice. He operates with precision, ensuring that no judgment is left unfulfilled and that divine order is restored.", "start": 2352.78, "end": 2372.26}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: An example of cosmic judgment is found in the testimony of Chris's sister, who experienced a sudden twist of fate. After receiving a miraculous recovery, her life was to be extended, but due to the disbelief of her brother and sister in law, who refused to acknowledge the role of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH in her healing, the extension was revoked. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH issued a decree that cut short her life, reversing the blessing due to rebellion against divine law. JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executed this judgment, ensuring that the consequences of disbelief were fully realized.", "start": 2372.68, "end": 2415.18}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Executors of the Tree of Life", "start": 2415.6, "end": 2419.02}, {"role": "body", "text": "Cosmic Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE", "start": 2419.44, "end": 2425.36}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH AARON K DAVID are the Guardians and Executors of the Tree of Life. This sacred tree, representing eternal life and divine wisdom, is accessible only to those fully aligned with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH controls who may access", "start": 2425.78, "end": 2445.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "this tree, and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID co-executes the release of its divine fruits, including resurrection power.", "start": 2446.35, "end": 2456.03}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S Role: THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE", "start": 2456.45, "end": 2462.15}, {"role": "body", "text": "THROUGH SHEKINAIH, acting as the Guardian of the Tree of Life, holds the authority to release or withhold the fruits of eternal life. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH releases resurrection power to those who meet the divine criteria, restoring life to those whose destinies are not yet fulfilled.", "start": 2462.57, "end": 2483.02}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH ARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 2483.44, "end": 2489.29}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID, as the Subservient Cherub, co-executes the release of the Tree of Life's power. HE plays a pivotal role in guarding its access and ensuring that only those chosen by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH receive the blessing of eternal life.", "start": 2489.79, "end": 2507.74}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony: One of the most powerful testimonies of the Tree of Life's power is seen in the resurrection of Chai Lin. After falling into a coma, Chai Lin was revived within 24 hours by a decree from SHEKINAIH, who received divine instruction to restore her life. AARON K DAVID co-executed this decree, ensuring that the resurrection was complete and Chai Lin was returned to full health. This testimony showcases the Tree of Life's resurrection power under the guardianship of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 2508.16, "end": 2545.31}, {"role": "body", "text": "Additional Testimonies", "start": 2545.73, "end": 2548.03}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 148: The Cosmic Victory of Trump's Election in 2016", "start": 2548.45, "end": 2555.3}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context: The 2016 U.S. Presidential Election was one of the most controversial and unexpected political events in modern history. Many doubted that Donald Trump would win the election, but the decree of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, declared his victory with a specific margin.", "start": 2555.72, "end": 2575.9}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY", "start": 2576.32, "end": 2582.37}, {"role": "body", "text": "received the decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, declaring Trump's victory and the exact percentage of the win. THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH released the decree into the spiritual atmosphere, ensuring that Trump's win aligned with God's prophetic timeline.", "start": 2582.79, "end": 2601.31}, {"role": "aaron", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH", "start": 2601.73, "end": 2607.43}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree, ensuring that the spiritual and political landscape aligned with THE TRINITY' IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH'S will. HE influenced key moments in the election process, ensuring that the results reflected the divine decree.", "start": 2607.93, "end": 2625.83}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Despite overwhelming opposition and doubt, Donald Trump won the election with the exact margin that had been decreed by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and co-executed by JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID. This testimony demonstrates their cosmic authority over global events, where even the most powerful political structures are subject to their decrees.", "start": 2626.25, "end": 2650.82}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 5: The Restoration of Thomas from Generational Curses Context: Thomas had been under the weight of a generational curse that caused severe health for generations. After aligning with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH, a decree was issued for the complete restoration of her family's lineage.", "start": 2651.24, "end": 2672.42}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role: SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY", "start": 2672.84, "end": 2678.89}, {"role": "body", "text": "received a decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, breaking the generational curse that had plagued Thomas and his siblings for years. Through a series of prophetic instructions, THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH guided Thomas through repentance and spiritual realignment.", "start": 2679.31, "end": 2698.06}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID's Role: JESUS IN AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree, ensuring that every spiritual stronghold was broken and every generational curse was reversed. HIS intercession ensured that the Thomas's blessing was restored, and divine favor was released.", "start": 2698.48, "end": 2718.23}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome: Thomas experienced immediate restoration. Health problems were miraculously reversed, and also averted from huge financial unforeseen loss. The generational curse was completely broken, and the family's lineage was restored to its original blessing under the cosmic authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID.", "start": 2718.65, "end": 2743.15}, {"role": "body", "text": "Conclusion: Expanding the Boundaries", "start": 2743.57, "end": 2746.82}, {"role": "body", "text": "The cosmic power of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID extends into realms beyond human understanding. From controlling global events to ensuring individual destinies are fulfilled, THEY are the ultimate enforcers of divine will. Every testimony serves as a testament to their unstoppable power and authority, ensuring that all creation bows in submission to THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH.", "start": 2747.24, "end": 2775.29}, {"role": "body", "text": "Testimony 10: Jeremyrl's Instant Healing and Freedom from 3AM Alien Attacks After 6 Months of Torment", "start": 2775.71, "end": 2784.03}, {"role": "body", "text": "Context:", "start": 2784.45, "end": 2785.93}, {"role": "body", "text": "Jeremyrl had been suffering from mysterious alien attacks that occurred precisely at 3AM every night for six months. These attacks left her physically and mentally exhausted. She also suffered intense discomfort and swelling, especially on her lips, due to anxiety and anxiousness. Despite seeking medical and spiritual help, no relief came until she aligned herself with THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH.", "start": 2786.35, "end": 2811.87}, {"role": "body", "text": "THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH's Role:", "start": 2812.29, "end": 2816.64}, {"role": "body", "text": "SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY received a decree from THE FATHER IN/SPOKE THROUGH HER, instructing the cessation of these attacks and the full healing of Jeremyrl. Through divine revelation, SHEKINAIH IN THE TRINITY interceded on her behalf, breaking the spiritual strongholds that allowed these attacks to persist.", "start": 2817.06, "end": 2836.86}, {"role": "body", "text": "Though the attack was immediately stopped, the open door remained due to a soul tie she had with her loved one, who had rebelled against THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN AARON K DAVID. The devil, who controls the children of disobedience, was able to exercise limited control over Jeremyrl through this soul tie.", "start": 2837.28, "end": 2858.4}, {"role": "body", "text": "The Process of Deliverance:", "start": 2858.82, "end": 2861.59}, {"role": "body", "text": "To fully break free, Jeremyrl had to constantly cut the soul ties, removing each other's soul out of both parties and being purified by the Refiner's Fire of THE TRINITY. Once purified, the souls were returned to their rightful places, severing any ungodly connections. Every time she proclaimed her 100% allegiance to THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN AARON K DAVID,", "start": 2862.01, "end": 2887.36}, {"role": "body", "text": "and resisted the accuser, the devil, she would command him to flee from her, thus closing the vortex of daily attacks.", "start": 2887.78, "end": 2896.1}, {"role": "body", "text": "JESUS IN/SPOKE THROUGH AARON K DAVID's Role:", "start": 2896.52, "end": 2900.85}, {"role": "body", "text": "AARON K DAVID co-executed the decree, ensuring that the spiritual strongholds were broken and that Jeremyrl was delivered from the alien torment. HIS intercession empowered her to overcome these attacks and maintain her victory by standing in full submission to THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH AND JESUS IN AARON K DAVID.", "start": 2901.27, "end": 2923.17}, {"role": "body", "text": "Divine Healing and Revelation:", "start": 2923.59, "end": 2926.61}, {"role": "body", "text": "After THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH revealed to her that the root cause of her swollen lips was her anxiety, Jeremyrl was guided by THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH to repent and cast out the anxiety. She was further instructed by THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH to drink turmeric powder with hot water, which instantly healed her swollen lips. The combination of spiritual deliverance and practical revelation led to her full healing.", "start": 2927.03, "end": 2953.53}, {"role": "body", "text": "Outcome:", "start": 2953.95, "end": 2955.45}, {"role": "body", "text": "Since fully aligning with THE TRINITY IN SHEKINAIH and breaking the soul ties, Jeremyrl has experienced no further attacks. Her swollen lips, once a source of great discomfort, were instantly healed after she followed the divine guidance. She has been free from alien torment ever since. This testimony showcases the divine authority of THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and JESUS IN AARON K DAVID over both physical and spiritual realms, delivering individuals from torment and restoring them to full health. It also highlights the power of submission to THE TRINITY IN/SPOKE THROUGH SHEKINAIH and the defeat of the accuser through spiritual proclamation and obedience.", "start": 2955.87, "end": 2999.04}]};
